Salaam from 🇵🇰

Don't know who are these 23k people who disliked this song. These kind of people are creating mess, miscommunication and violence between 327k people who like each other.

After reading a lot of comments, listening and watching this song again n again, it would be unfair with the nationals of two great countries that this is a masterpiece. Every word is deep and meaningful. New generation / modern societies are running away from their culture which is the most important thing in any society. Western culture is killing all the teachings, respect, environment and happiness. I wish that somehow we could undo all these things and can become more cultural than modern. I wish...

In addition, The reason of separation was not to become enemies. The reason was only to just live under same societies and religion, which faded away because of religious extremists and politicians. Still we love our neighbour and I personally would like to visit India.
